description: Seafield Resources Ltd., a development stage company, engages in the exploration, development, and mining of mineral properties in South America. It primarily explores for gold ores, as well as for silver ores. It has a 100% interest in the Quinch√≠a gold project that includes 15 mining concessions covering an area of 6,042.8 hectares located in the Department of Risaralda, Colombia. The company also holds a 100% undivided interest in the Elora project that consists of 14 patented parcels of mining land and 1 license of occupation located in the Kenora Mining Division of Northwestern Ontario. Seafield Resources Ltd. was incorporated in 1957 and is based in Toronto, Canada.
ceo: Mr. David William Prins B.Eng. Tech
